<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/33601ABMMCLRHCDGJGLSCVTKRJSMDCMSS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Gal-entine's Day";
  schema:description """
	<h2></h2><span><br/></span>What's Galentine's Day? Oh, it's only the best day of the year.\" - Leslie Knope. Come and join us for a fun-filled night of Femme-tastic hilarity as we explore the delights and DRAMA of love and friendship with a cast of wickedly funny femmes!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 14A<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
