<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/30401AVTJMSJLDVLNKKKDPCPPRDDJCLRT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Improv for Two";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Valentine's Day Workshop!</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Time:</span> 3:30pm – 5:30pm<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ages:</span> 19+<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Level Required:</span> no improv experience required!<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Workshop Capacity:</span> 11 dynamic duos<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Cost:</span> $60 per pair<span><br/></span>Only 1 ticket is required per two people!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Do you and your partner want to try something new and fun on Valentine’s Day? Have you always wanted to try improv, but don’t want to try it alone? Already love improv, and want to get your friend into it? This is the perfect workshop for all of those things!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is a Valentine’s Special Workshop for two people to try improv together! Through many fun partner exercises, come enjoy a fun, friendly, and supportive environment to learn the magic of “Yes, And!”<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*The goal of this workshop is not to get into the weeds and learn about how to do perform improv, but more a chance to have fun and try something new with your favourite person!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Couples, situationships, friends, pals, duos, or some person you met off the street are all welcome. We will not exclude you if you aren't dating the person you're learning with. But do keep in mind we will not be pairing up strangers for this event.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All workshops and classes are 19+ only.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>LOCK OUT POLICY: Doors will lock 15 minutes after the class begins. Late comers will not be permitted.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-02-14T15:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/5c34a88e-9105-41ca-b099-f425aca4cdcf.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:f1e5d4ebb48e4f06bccb5a907ecb5f635473;
  schema:duration "PT120M";
  schema:endDate "2026-02-14T17:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

