<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/33602AVCPSGVMCVCNMHMPNRDVKCDDPRTR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "My Funny Valentines Show";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Laugh at love with us at The Improv Centre at one of our TWO SHOWS this Valentine's Day!</h2><span><br/></span>The best quality in a date? A sense of humour. This Valentine’s Day, ditch the pressure and do something a little more spontaneous with a night of romantic, ridiculous, completely improvised comedy. Inspired by audience suggestions, our performers create scenes about crushes, meet-cutes, long-term love, and  those awkward moments when something could have happened but never did.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re bringing a date, your long term partner, or flying solo, the best way to celebrate connection is with comedy. This show sells out every year, so don’t wait too long to make your move!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 14A<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-02-14T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/72665a55-86ee-438f-9e80-84594f5bb3a8.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:f1e5d4ebb48e4f06bccb5a907ecb5f635475;
