<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/43201AJDRNMMDNNQTNJHJVCVNCQGVJMVN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Games Lab";
  schema:description """
	In this class we will explore a series of classic short form games, giving you the space to play, play, and play some more! Get key tips and tricks on how to be even more successful in your scene work as you learn about different types of improv games and the \"motors\" that make them so much fun to play!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*This class is for improvisors with some experience. If you are new to improv, check out our Beginner's Classes!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All workshops and classes are 19+ only.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>14 spots available per class
""";
