  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Theatresports";
  schema:description """
	Two teams of highly skilled improv comedians vie for the laughs and support of audience judges. A high-energy, fast-paced, and good-natured competition that will leave you wanting more! Our company has been performing Theatresports for over 40 years! No two shows are alike. Expect to laugh harder than you've ever laughed before!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
