<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/14804AVGLDTNBPVMGTNPDGRPNVTPLHJBB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Twist of Fate";
  schema:description """
	This fast-paced battle of wits is not just any ordinary improv show! Our hilarious hosts will constantly stir the pot – adding points, spinning challenge wheels, swapping teams, and throwing unexpected curveballs that push the limits of our performers' improvisational skills. From ridiculous on-the-spot games to wild, skill-testing challenges no two moments are ever the same!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
